lyrics:
[Verse]
Dark clouds surround me, overhead they loom
Rain falling down, sweeping away the gloom
The thunder's roar becomes my battleground
Embracing the storm, a melody profound

[Chorus]
Rainy day, drenching my soul with the tears I've cried
Rainy day, the rhythm of sorrow crashes inside
Guitar strings weep, as the thunder roars its might
Rainy day, a cathartic symphony of the night
